    "To enhance the productivity of the systems (e.g., classification or prediction), machine learning (ML) practitioners often strategically combine or fuse the models called Ensemble of models.",
    "In addition to enhancing the reliability Fig. 8 General CNN based architecture used to establish GAN model of a model's conviction, ensemble learning is employed for a wide variety of other tasks, including feature selection, data fusion, incremental learning, non-stationary learning, error correction, and the selection of optimal features.",
    "Ensemble techniques in statistics and machine learning combine many learning algorithms to achieve greater prediction performance than each of the component learning algorithms alone.",
    "In comparison to a single GAN, an ensemble of GANs can now more correctly reflect the distribution of normal data specially Deepfake identification [53].",
    "Mathematical formulation used in CNN and GAN• Convolution operation:where I is the input image, K is the convolutional kernel, and * denotes the convolution operation.• Activation function where σ is activation function, K is the convolutional kernel and b is bias term."
